            Rachel Orzechowski
          
          
            
              I am an aquatic ecologist specializing in dreissenid
              mussels based in the Great Lakes region. Currently I work
              with the Elgin Lab as a NOAA Affiliate. I enjoy hiking,
              camping, and drinking too much coffee.
